  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription(askerIsNull==true)->We've intercepted messages about the location of an old ruin complex near [map_definite]. These ruins can contain anything, from cryptosleep caskets and archotech artifacts to rare weapons and armor.\n\nBe careful, as these ancient ruins are certainly defended by a number of threats. We should be prepared for anything.</li>

